{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase minimum wage to \u00a315 per hour",
        "additional_details": "We want young adults and those suffering from the brink of poverty to be able to acclimatise better to the growing financial difficulties. We think raising the minimum wage to \u00a315/hour  allows for those who can work to assist the country as a whole. In our view it can improve the aspect of fundamental tasks of life which ensures an enhanced quality of living amongst the population.",
        "background": "Due to the current crisis as well as the rapid rate of inflation, we believe it is necessary for the standard minimum wage for those who are 18 and over to be brought up to a liveable \u00a315 per hour.",
